---
description: Design language
alwaysApply: true
---

DarkVector should feel calm, premium and modern.

Inspired by:

- Raycast
- Cursor
- Linear
- Arc

Avoid:

- Hacker aesthetics
- Cyberpunk
- Government dashboards
- Excessive badges
- Visual clutter

Use whitespace intentionally.

Motion communicates hierarchy.

Every page should have one primary focus.

The investigation is always the hero.
